About Me

Ahmed Montaser — Video Editor

I’m Ahmed Montaser, a short-form video editor based in Cairo. I help creators and brands tell their stories through high-energy videos that match today’s fast-scrolling world. With a focus on TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube Shorts, I turn concepts into visuals that connect and convert.
